      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://linguage.github.io/terencetao/writing-guide/zh/motivate-the-paper.zh/&#34;&gt;中文版本&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;div&#xA;  class=&#34;link-card group relative my-3 w-full overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-[var(--lc-border,rgba(15,23,42,0.12))] bg-[var(--lc-bg,var(--card-bg,var(--surface,#ffffff))))] transition-shadow duration-150 hover:shadow-[var(--lc-shadow-hover,0_14px_30px_-18px_rgba(15,23,42,0.35))]&#34;&#xA;  data-url=&#34;https://terrytao.wordpress.com/advice-on-writing-papers/motivate-the-paper/&#34;&#xA;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a&#xA;    class=&#34;link-card__fallback block px-4 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--lc-url,var(--link-color,#0e6a85))] underline-offset-4 hover:underline&#34;&#xA;    href=&#34;https://terrytao.wordpress.com/advice-on-writing-papers/motivate-the-paper/&#34;&#xA;    target=&#34;_blank&#34;&#xA;    rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;  &gt;&#xA;    https://terrytao.wordpress.com/advice-on-writing-papers/motivate-the-paper/&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h1 id=&#34;motivate-the-paper&#34;&gt;Motivate the paper&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;A scrupulous writer, in every sentence that he writes, will ask himself at least four questions, thus:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;What am I trying to say?&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;What words will express it?&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;What image or idiom will make it clearer?&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Is this image fresh enough to have an effect?&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;George Orwell, &amp;ldquo;Politics and the English Language&amp;rdquo;, 1946&lt;/p&gt;</description>
